    • Class it.polimi.ingsw.am43.Model.Player

      class Player extends Object implements Serializable
      serialVersionUID:
      4739584014082362305L

      • Serialized Fields

        • deployed
          ArrayList<CardSide> deployed
          A list of CardSides that represents the player's deployed cards. The player deploys cards, but for the sake of the mere functionality, only the placed (and displayed) CardSides are stored, since are the ones used for the computation of resources and score.
        • in_hand
          PlayableCard[] in_hand
          An array of PlayableCards that represents the player's hand, dealt at the beginning of the game.
        • pawn_color
          PawnColor pawn_color
          Player's PawnColor.
        • personal_objective
          ObjectiveCard personal_objective
          The player's secret objective.
        • placements
          int[][] placements
          A matrix of CardSides that represents the player's placements. The matrix is actually of integers, with every element being -1 if empty and an integer otherwise. The integer is the deployedID of a CardSide. By doing so, the deployedIDs always increase, and it is possible to effortlessly understand which card is on top of the other, the order of placement and much more.
        • res_qty
          int[] res_qty
          The array that stores the number of resources obtained by the player. The resources are ordered as follows: Animal, Insect, Fungi, Plant, Inkwell, Quill, Manuscript
        • score
          int score
          Player's score.
        • startingCard
          PlayableCard startingCard
          The starting card of the player, dealt at the beginning of the game.
        • username
          String username
          Player's username.
